  "problemBrief": "MakeMyTrip's Bookings per DAU dropped 13% over 60 days. DAU grew 15% to 11.5M. Total bookings are flat at 820K/day. Revenue fell 16.5%. The CEO wants a full root cause brief before Friday's board meeting. Your job: find what is actually broken and propose solutions that move the metric.",
  "scenarioContext": "MakeMyTrip recently expanded its homestay inventory by 340%, launched an international travel push targeting Vietnam, Japan, and South Korea, and completed a UI refresh that removed several advanced search filters. DAU growth is being driven by a new user acquisition campaign. The product team believes this is a temporary dip. The finance team believes something structural has broken.",
